Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.79,0:01:35.67,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1910BD&}Želim plastično srce.\N{\3c&H6A9800&}(Plus! Plus! Ali onda minus!)
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.67,0:01:42.92,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H42009A&\c&HD7B8FF&}demo sore ja tsumaranai soko ni kizuita mono kachi
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.67,0:01:42.92,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H42009A&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ali to je dosadno, kada bih primetila, pobedila bih.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.59,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HBCD3FF&}koi wa amakute nigai mono
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.59,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ljubav je slatka i gorka stvar,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.90,0:01:51.72,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFF4C5&}tanjunmeikai fukuzatsukaiki na shiromono
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.90,0:01:51.72,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFFFFF&}prosta je i jednostavna, složena i zagonetna.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.91,0:01:54.76,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H007D9C&\c&HBBE5F2&}dou demo ii koto bakkari ki ni shitari suru no
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.91,0:01:54.76,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H007D9C&\c&HFFFFFF&}Samo se brinem o svakakvim stvarima.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.60,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HD8D5FF&\3c&H1910BD&}donna kanji? sonna kanji!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.60,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1910BD&\c&HFFFFFF&}Kakav je osećaj? Takav je osećaj!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.77,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H42009A&\c&HD7B8FF&}onkoutokujitsu ekisentorikku na anata
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.77,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H42009A&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ti si ljubazan i iskren, ali ekscentričan.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.80,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HBCD3FF&}tsuyogaru suburi wo zenshin matotte tachiuchi
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.80,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HFFFFFF&}Pravim se da sam snažna i takmičim se sa tobom.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.61,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFF4C5&}sunao na dake da to shigeki ga tsuyokute kurakura
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.61,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFFFFF&}Samo od toga što sam iskrena osećam se ošamućeno.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.88,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H007D9C&\c&HBBE5F2&}kizutsuichau no  kizutsukechau no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.88,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H007D9C&\c&HFFFFFF&}Povređena sam, povredila sam te.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.11,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HD8D5FF&\3c&H1910BD&}junjou purepara-to
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.11,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1910BD&\c&HFFFFFF&}Naivna priprema.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.87,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H42009A&\c&HD7B8FF&}atama no naka wa   {\3c&H6A9800&\c&HE8FFB3&}(itsumo hitori no)
